  "summary": {
    "en": "A 120-piece glow fort kit for night play, STEM building, and gift-ready imaginative construction.",
    "zh": "120件夜光堡垒拼搭套装，适合夜间玩法、STEM搭建和礼品化创意建构。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "Glow-in-the-dark rods add a stronger play effect after charging under light, making the set attractive for bedrooms and themed gifts.",
      "The 120-piece configuration supports castles, towers, tents, tunnels, and other repeatable frame structures.",
      "PP components are lightweight, durable, and easy for children to connect, remove, and rebuild.",
      "Color-box packaging and accessory planning make the item suitable for retail, e-commerce, event gifts, and OEM/ODM cooperation."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "夜光杆件吸光后带来更强的玩耍效果，适合卧室场景和主题礼品。",
      "120件配置可支持城堡、高塔、帐篷、通道等多种可重复框架结构。",
      "PP组件轻便耐用，儿童可轻松连接、拆卸和重新搭建。",
      "彩盒包装和配件配置完整，适合零售、电商、活动礼品和OEM/ODM合作。"
    ]
  },
